Russia RTS Stock-Index Futures Gain 0.2% at Start of Trading

-- B y   H a l i a   P a v l i v a
-- 
2011-05-04T15:05:11Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-04/russia-rts-stock-index-futures-gain-0-2-at-start-of-trading.html
Russia ’s RTS futures expiring in June
added 0.2 percent to 191,005 at 11:00 a.m. in  New York .  Contracts on OAO Gazprom, the natural-gas export monopoly,
OAO Lukoil, the country’s second-biggest oil producer, and OAO
Sberbank, Russia’s largest lender, climbed 0.2 percent.  The Market Vectors Russia ETF, a U.S.-traded fund that
holds Russian shares, dropped 1.9 percent.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Halia Pavliva in New York at 
 hpavliva@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alexander Nicholson at 
 anicholson6@bloomberg.net  